com.foreach.across.modules.graphql.entity.configuration

Class EntityGraphQLSchemaConfiguration<ENTITY_TYPE>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.graphql.entity.configuration.EntityGraphQLSchemaConfiguration<ENTITY_TYPE>

  • public class EntityGraphQLSchemaConfiguration<ENTITY_TYPE>
extends Object
    Represents the GraphQL schema configuration that should be applied to subset of entities. The subset is identified by the entityConfigurationPredicate. Used by the GraphQLSchemaFactory to generated an actual GraphQLSchema instance.
    Author:
    Maaike Hellemans
    See Also:
    GraphQLSchemaFactory
